\s SHENGERO RY’IMANA BAGENZI
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Shengero ry’Imana bagenzi, shimagiza Yesu Mukiza, n’Umukiza w’abari mw’isi, kandi n’Umwami w’amahoro.\bd*
\pc \bdit Yesu Mwami n’utuzigame, turongore mu ngendo zacu.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Hanga rihambaye ry’Imana, muce mw’Irembo rifunganye, mwubake ku masezerano, nk’ukw’Aburahamu yagenjeje.\bd*
\pc \bdit Yesu Mwami n’utuzigame, turongore mu ngendo zacu.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Yemwe abavutse ubwa kabiri, mwitwararik’ivyo mw’ijuru, ntimwitwararik’\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd ivy’iyi si, kukw’ivy’isi ari ibizoshira.\bd*
\pc \bdit Yesu Mwami n’utuzigame, turongore mu ngendo zacu.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Twambar’ivyambarwa vya Mpwemu, twitwaze n’inkota y’Imana, tugende nk’abana b’umuco, twiyambure ivy’uyu mubiri.\bd*
\pc \bdit Yesu Mwami n’utuzigame, turongore mu ngendo zacu.\bdit*\bd  \bd*
